1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,400
Your attention is a limited battery.

2
00:00:02,400 --> 00:00:07,200
Just like your phone, your brain has a finite amount of focus.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:09,600
This concept is called selective attention.

4
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:11,600
It’s how you prioritize information.

5
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:14,800
Cognitive load affects how much you can focus.

6
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:15,600
More distractions?

7
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:16,800
More mental drain.

8
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:20,400
So, if you feel drained, it’s not your fault.

9
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:22,800
You’re just managing your brain’s battery.

10
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:25,200
Want to save your brain's battery?

11
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:26,800
Follow for more tips!
